eact%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20someone%20wanting%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20and%20not%20work.%20I%20completely%20respect%20that%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-dream-job-to-be-stay-at-home-dad-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estaying%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20someone%20happy%2C%20that's%20wonderful.%20But%20that's%20not%20me.%20I've%20always%20wanted%20to%20work%2C%20not%20just%20for%20financial%20reasons%2C%20but%20because%20it's%20part%20of%20who%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20subtle%20remarks%20and%20comments%20from%20my%20in-laws%20started%20to%20weigh%20on%20me%20because%20I%20saw%20how%20they%20were%20shaping%20my%20kids'%20ideas%20about%20what%20men%20and%20women%20should%20or%20shouldn't%20do.%20They%20were%20lessons%20my%20kids%20were%20absorbing%20every%20day%20about%20responsibility%2C%20respect%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubtle-ways-women-treated-differently-work-2014-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egender%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22090a082f-59fb-4e8a-8df6-087b67362731%5C%22%3EFinally%2C%20standing%20my%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStanding%20my%20ground%20came%20with%20struggles.%20There%20were%20disagreements%2C%20subtle%20comments%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassive-aggressive-in-laws-paying-for-vacation-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etension%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sometimes%20hung%20in%20the%20air%20for%20days.%20There%20were%20hardly%20ever%20dramatic%20arguments%20%E2%80%94%20more%20often%2C%20it%20was%20quiet%20disapproval%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20is%20felt%20more%20than%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20was%20supportive%2C%20but%20sometimes%20caught%20in%20the%20middle.%20He'd%20grown%20up%20with%20the%20same%20traditional%20ideas%2C%20and%20while%20he%20understood%20me%20and%20my%20beliefs%2C%20he%20also%20felt%20torn%20between%20keeping%20peace%20at%20home