heng%20Xin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple's%20iOS%2026%20will%20allow%20users%20to%20filter%20out%20texts%20from%20unknown%20senders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20could%20be%20a%20big%20financial%20problem%20for%20campaigns%20that%20rely%20on%20texts%20for%20donations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20GOP%20group%20is%20warning%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20%24500%20million%20loss%20for%20GOP%20campaigns%20overall.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple's%3C%2Fa%3E%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-stop-spam-texts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espam%20text%3C%2Fa%3E%20filtering%20feature%20could%20end%20up%20being%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20headache%20for%20political%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-iphone-ios-26-features-liquid-glass-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EiOS%2026%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20a%20new%20feature%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20filter%20text%20messages%20from%20unrecognized%20numbers%20into%20an%20%26quot%3BUnknown%20Senders%26quot%3B%20folder%20without%20sending%20a%20notification.%20Users%20can%20then%20go%20to%20that%20filter%20and%20hit%20%26quot%3BMark%20as%20Known%26quot%3B%20or%20delete%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memo%20seen%20by%20BI%20and%20first%20reported%20by%20Punchbowl%20News%2C%20the%20official%20campaign%20committee%20in%20charge%20of%20electing%20GOP%20senators%20warned%20that%20the%20new%20feature%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20steep%20drop%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20change%20has%20profound%20implications%20for%20our%20ability%20to%20fundraise%2C%20mobilize%20voters%2C%20and%20run%20digital%20campaigns%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20a%20July%2024%20memo%20from%20the%20National%20Republican%20Senatorial%20Committee%2C%20or%20NRSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20estimated%20that%20the%20new%20feature%20could%20cost%20the%20group%20%2425%20million%20in%20lost%20revenue%20and%20lead%20to%20a%20%24500%20million%20loss%20for%20GOP%20campaigns%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20based%20on%20the%20estimate%20that%2070%25%20of%20small-dollar%20donations%20come%20from%20text%20messages%20and%20that%20iPhones%20make%20up%2060%25%20of%20mobile%20devices%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20some%20people%20may%20choose%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20campaign's%20text%20messages%2C%20individuals%20often%20get%20texts%20from%20campaigns%20that%20they%20didn't%20sign%20up%20for%2C%20but%20who%20purchased%20a%20contact%20list%20from%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampaigns%20in%20both%20parties%20rely%20on%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoliticians-desperate-fundraising-appeals-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esometimes%20unsolicited%20text%20messages%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20just%20for%20fundraising%2C%20but%20for%20voter%20turnout%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnilaterally%20blocking%20campaigns%20and%20political%20parties%20from%20being%20able%20to%20contact%20voters%20with%20get-out-the-vote%20or%20persuasive%20messaging%20is%20voter%20disenfranchisement%2C%26quot%3B%20Joanna%20Rodriguez%2C%20a%20spokeswoman%20for%20the%20NRSC%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20critical%20Apple%20delay%20their%20rollout%20of%20this%20feature%20until%20these%20concerns%20have%20been%20addressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EiOS%2026%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20rolled%20out%20in%20mid-September.%20Apple%20senior%20executive%20Darin%20Adler%20said%20at%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-wwdc-conference-keynote-event-live-updates-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWorldwide%20Developers%20Conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%20that%20users%20using%20the%20feature%20%26quot%3Bwould%20continue%20to%20see%20important%20time-sensitive%20messages%26quot%3B%20like%20verification%20codes%20and%20scheduling-related%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdler%20characterized%20the%20new%20feature%20as%20giving%20users%20%26quot%3Btotal%20control%20over%20who%20appears%20in%20your%20conversation%20list.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NRSC%20memo%20also%20said%20that%20lobbyists%20and%20trade%20groups%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Basleep%20at%20the%20wheel%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20new%20feature%20and%20that%20Apple%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20engaging.%26quot%3B%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20company%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20left%20before%20the%20public%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20memo.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20going%20to%20push%20back%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20now.%20We%20have%20a%20very%20narrow%20window%20to%20fix%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Nellis%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Democratic%20digital%20fundraising%20firm%20Authentic%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20members%20of%20his%20party%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20take%20this%20seriously%2C%20but%20good-faith%20actors%20won't%20see%20as%20much%20of%20a%20hit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20panicking%20about%20losing%20%24500%20million%20in%20revenue%2C%20it%20probably%20means%20you%20were%20scamming%20people%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Nellis%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can't%20raise%20money%20online%20without%20misleading%20your%20supporters%2C%20you%20deserve%20what%20you%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENellis%20also%20said%20the%20change%20underscores%20why%20campaigns%20need%20to%20have%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20fundraising%20and%20communication%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there's%20a%20regulatory%2C%20product%2C%20or%20voter%20shift%2C%20you%20still%20need%20reliable%20ways%20to%20reach%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Nellis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw