n%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-wet-dry-vacuums%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20wet-dry%20vacuums%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20without%20needing%20to%20revisit%20the%20dock%2C%20show%20a%20lot%20of%20promise%20for%20even%20better%20performance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMop%20lifting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20lot%20of%20mid-range%20to%20premium-priced%20robots%20advertise%20being%20able%20to%20lift%20damp%20mopping%20pads%20during%20the%20cleaning%20process.%20We've%20found%20that%20most%20of%20those%20still%20drag%20or%20touch%20on%20medium%20pile%20carpet%20and%20rugs.%20The%20Shark%20PowerDetect%20NeverTouch%20Pro%20is%20one%20example%20that%20did%20a%20great%20job%20of%20angling%20its%20mop%20pad%20to%20avoid%20touching.%20The%20best%20solution%20here%20for%20delicate%20rugs%20is%20to%20look%20for%20a%20unit%20that%20can%20automatically%20detach%20its%20mopping%20pads%20in%20its%20station%20or%20vacuum%20before%20mopping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavigation%20tech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Smarter%20mapping%20leads%20to%20more%20efficient%20cleaning%20and%20better%20coverage.%20Most%20companies%20have%20coalesced%20around%20LiDAR%20technology%2C%20which%20bounces%20light%20off%20objects%20to%20map%20rooms%2C%20but%20none%20are%20exactly%20the%20same.%20We've%20found%20Roborock%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20at%20mapping%20and%20object%20avoidance%2C%20as%20its%20newest%20devices%20each%20year%20have%20more%20insights%20into%20the%20environment%20around%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintenance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Especially%20with%20a%20mopping%20combo%20unit%2C%20the%20first%20step%20to%20reducing%20manual%20maintenance%20is%20to%20get%20a%20unit%20with%20a%20self-emptying%20base%20station%20with%20water%20reservoirs.%20Adding%20air%20drying%20and%20other%20automated%20features%20can%20further%20push%20off%20the%20time%20that%20regular%20maintenance%20happens.%20Units%20without%20self-cleaning%20or%20warm%20air%20drying%20will%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20directly%20after%20each%20mopping%20cycle%20to%20prevent%20any%20mold%20growth%20or%20bacteria%20from%20forming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDust%20bin%20and%20water%20tank%20size%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20larger%20tank%20can%20clean%20more%20space%20without%20refilling.%20Although%20this%20aspect%20is%20worth%20considering%2C%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20models%20we've%20tested%20provided%20at%20least%20a%20week%20of%20modest%20mopping%20without%20needing%20to%20return.%20The%20self-cleaning%20robots%20have%20separate%20clean%20and%20dirty%20water%20tanks%3B%20the%20clean%20tanks%20are%20for%20mopping%20water%20and%20flushing%20the%20mop%20pads%2C%20while%20the%20dirty%20water%20tanks%20collect%20all%20the%20dirty%20water%20from%20the%20cleaning%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20coolest%20features%20will%20cost%20extra%2C%20but%20they%20can%20add%20new%20dimensions%20to%20your%20robot%20experience.%20The%20Saros%2010R%20can%20patrol%20your%20house%2C%20without%20cleaning%20and%20use%20its%20camera%20for%20surveillance.%20This%20could%20be%20used%20for%20checking%20in%20on%20an%20animal%2C%20instead%20of%20buying%20a%20dedicated%20pet%20cam.%20Using%20voice%20assistants%20to%20initiate%20cleaning%20tasks%20is%20a%20popular%20bonus%20feature%2C%20although%20I've%20rarely%20had%20success%20remembering%20the%20exact%20commands%20or%20when%20to%20use%20them.%20The%20latest%20trend%20is%20to%20inject%20AI%20into%20robot%20cleaning.%20The%20most%20common%20is%20determining%20what%20rooms%20need%20to%20be%20cleaned%2C%20how%20often%2C%20and%20with%20which%20settings%2C%20or%20dirt%20detection%20features%2C%20like%20the%20ability%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20floor%20is%20clean%20based%20on%20water%20color.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20getting%20harder%20to%20avoid%20having%20the%20devices%20take%20over%20the%20cleaning%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0de8d9f-e86a-4f9a-ac74-2d23b8295d8f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22six%20robot%20vacuums%20lined%20up%20against%20the%20wall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883edee85e81483682ebb04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221228%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20evaluating%20how%20these%20robots%20handle%20various%20debris%20and%20spills%20on%20hard%20flooring%20and%20carpets%2C%20we%20also%20consider%20how%20well%20it%20navigates%20a%20space%20and%20avoids%20obstacles%2C%20noise%2C%20battery%20life%20and%20try%20its%20special%20features%20like%20self-cleaning%20and%20scheduling.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20testing%20and%20writing%20about%20tech%20products%20since%202013.%20Since%20the%20rise%20of%20smart%20home%20appliances%2C%20I've%20covered%20dozens%20of%20robot%20vacuums.%20In%20addition%20to%20testing%20them%20and%20putting%20them%20through%20their%20paces%2C%20I've%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20talk%20with%20company%20representatives%20about%20these%20machines%20and%20ask%20probing%20questions.%20I've%20talked%20with%20consumers%20about%20these%20products%20to%20better%20understand%20their%20experiences%20and%20what's%20important%20to%20them.%20Either%20I%20or%20members%20of%20the%20Business%20Insider%20Reviews%20team%20have%20personally%20used%20all%20of%20these%20models%20we%20evaluated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECarpet%20cleaning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20poured%20a%20tablespoon%20each%20of%20flour%2C%20coffee%20grounds%2C%20and%20kitty%20litter%20(or%20crushed%20cereal)%20on%2018-inch-square%20sections%20of%20carpeting.%20We%20also%20collected%20hair%20to%20place%20on%20the%20carpeting.%20We%20ran%20the%20vacuums%20on%20their%20most%20powerful%20mode%20for%20two%20cleaning%20cycles%20and%20compared%20before-and-after%20photos%20to%20estimate%20the%20percentage%20of%20each%20material%20picked%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardwood%20floor%20cleaning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20is%20the%20same%20as%20the%20carpet%20cleaning%20test%20on%20hardwood%20flooring.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorner%20cleaning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20poured%20a%20teaspoon%20of%20flour%20in%20a%204-inch%20radius%20in%20a%20hardwood%20corner.%20We%20photographed%20the%20messes%20before%20and%20after%20running%20the%20robot%20vacuums%20for%20two%20cleaning%20cycles%20to%20compare%20how%20much%20flour%20was%20left%20and%20how%20close%20to%20the%20corner%20each%20unit%20got.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMopping%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20testing%20robots%20with%20mopping%20capabilities%2C%20we%20poured%20two%20ounces%20of%20sugary%20soda%20on%20linoleum%20and%20allowed%20it%20to%20dry%20overnight.%20Then%2C%20we%20compared%20photos%20before%20and%20after%20running%20the%20vacuums%20through%20two%20mopping%20cycles%20to%20determine%20how%20much%20soda%20they%20picked%20up.%20We%20also%20noted%20if%20the%20floor%20was%20sticky%20afterward.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EObstacle%20avoidance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20stuck%20robot%20vacuum%20is%20annoying%20because%20you%20need%20to%20intervene%20to%20get%20it%20unstuck.%20Meanwhile%2C%20it%20makes%20error%20sounds%20and%20sends%20you%20notifications.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20running%20over%20a%20charging%20cable%20or%20sock%20can%20ruin%20both%20the%20robot%20and%20your%20items.%20Our%20test%20areas%20feature%20several%20obstacles%2C%20including%20stairs%20and%20a%20table%20with%20chairs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20used%20a%20sound%20meter%20to%20measure%20the%20decibel%20output%20of%20the%20vacuums%20from%2012%20inches%20away%20as%20they%20ran%20on%20the%20lowest%20and%20highest%20settings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20ran%20each%20fully%20charged%20unit%20on%20its%20highest%20setting%20during%20long%20cleaning%20runs.%20Then%2C%20based%20on%20the%20time%20consumed%20and%20percentage%20remaining%2C%20we%20calculated%20the%20actual%20runtime%20to%20ensure%20it%20matched%20the%20manufacturer's%20estimates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Scheduling%20and%20automatically%20returning%20to%20the%20charging%20dock%20are%20must-have%20features.%20All%20of%20the%20tested%20bots%20include%20these%20features.%20We%20also%20looked%20for%20common%20higher-end%20options%2C%20including%20no-go%20zone%20programming%2C%20zoned%20cleaning%2C%20multi-floor%20mapping%2C%20self-emptying%20docks%2C%20self-cleaning%2C%20and%20home%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221539f0af-2585-438e-84ea-ef07788993cc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERobot%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20FAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20a%20robot%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20combo%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20combo%20is%20a%20device%20that%20can%20perform%20both%20cleaning%20functions.%20Generally%2C%20these%20combo%20units%20can%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20simultaneously%2C%20or%20do%20them%20in%20various%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20robot%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20combos%20safe%20for%20hardwood%20floors%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20devices%20can%20be%20used%20with%20pretty%20much%20every%20kind%20of%20flooring.%20The%20higher-end%20models%20can%20detect%20the%20type%20of%20flooring%20they're%20working%20on%20and%20adjust%20their%20mopping%20pressure%20and%20water%20usage.%20Other%20models%20can%20be%20manually%20adjusted%20in%20the%20app.%20I've%20used%20all%20of%20these%20models%20on%20real%20hardwood%20floors%20and%20never%20had%20one%20scratch%20or%20damage%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20a%20robot%20mop%20replace%20manual%20mopping%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20robot%20mops%20possess%20incredible%20cleaning%20performance%2C%20they%20likely%20aren't%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20mops%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20these%20machines%20are%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20consistent%20pressure%2C%20water%20flow%2C%20and%20rotating%20pads%2C%20so%20they%20may%20be%20better%20than%20doing%20a%20whole%20area%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20you%20should%20still%20hold%20on%20to%20a%20mop%20for%20cleaning%20tight%20areas%20like%20bathrooms%20or%20for%20heavy-duty%20targeted%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20robot%20mop%20vacuums%20clean%20carpets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combo%20units%20will%20clean%20hard%20flooring%2C%20carpet%2C%20and%20rugs.%20The%20robots%20try%20to%20avoid%20wetting%20carpet%20and%20rugs%20by%20lifting%20their%20damp%20pads%2C%20vacuuming%20carpet%20first%2C%20before%20wetting%20the%20mop%20pads%2C%20or%20leaving%20damp%20mop%20pads%20behind%20at%20their%20base%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%20should%20I%20clean%20the%20mop%20pad%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20unit%20like%20the%20Roomba%20205%2C%20which%20doesn't%20have%20a%20base%20station%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20manually%20clean%20the%20mop%20pad%20after%20each%20use%20by%20removing%20it%20and%20washing%20it%20in%20the%20sink.%20The%20higher-end%20units%20will%20clean%20the%20mopping%20pads%20with%20either%20cold%2C%20warm%2C%20or%20hot%20water%2C%20and%20then%20dry%20them%20with%20cool%20or%20hot%20air%20to%20avoid%20mold%20and%20bacteria.%20For%20those%20models%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20ever%20manually%20clean%20the%20mopping%20pads%2C%20but%20you%20will%20need%20to%20empty%20the%20dirty%20water%20tanks%20and%20regularly%20wipe%20the%20base%20station%20of%20any%20accumulated%20dirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines