0submarines%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20be%20targeted%20for%20attack.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarines%20just%20wrapped%20up%20a%20training%20exercise%20that%20saw%20troops%20tossing%20sonobuoys%20out%20of%20the%20back%20of%20MV-22%20Osprey%20tiltrotor%20aircraft%2C%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20meant%20to%20boost%20how%20the%20Marines%20and%20Navy%20can%20work%20together%20to%20fight%20enemy%20submarines.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20past%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20can%20contribute%20to%20ASW%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Navy%20Capt.%20Bill%20Howey%2C%20director%20of%20maritime%20operations%20for%20Commander%2C%20Submarine%20Group%20Two%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20the%20training.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we're%20refining%20how%20they%20contribute%20and%20then%20integrating%20that%20into%20the%20fleet%20playbook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnti-submarine%20warfare%20(ASW)%20involves%20detecting%2C%20tracking%2C%20and%20neutralizing%20enemy%20submarines%20using%20specialized%20ships%2C%20aircraft%2C%20sonar%20systems%2C%20and%20underwater%20weapons.%20It%20is%20a%20critical%20component%20of%20naval%20defense%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20fleets%20and%20strategic%20waterways%20from%20hidden%20underwater%20threats%2C%20though%20it%20hasn't%20traditionally%20been%20a%20mission%20in%20which%20Marines%20have%20been%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpendable%20sonobuoys%2C%20like%20those%20used%20in%20the%20exercise%2C%20are%20launched%2C%20or%20in%20this%20case%20dropped%2C%20from%20the%20air%20(from%20fixed-wing%20and%20rotary-wing%20aircraft%20and%20uncrewed%20airborne%20platforms)%20and%20are%20used%20for%20detecting%20and%20tracking%20submarines.%20They%20can%20also%20help%20with%20targeting%20subs%20for%20a%20torpedo%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20training%20was%20part%20of%20a%20yearslong%20reshuffling%20for%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20from%20fighting%20counterinsurgency%20warfare%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20toward%20peer-level%20warfare%20against%20adversarial%20nations%20like%20China%20or%20Russia.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20among%20the%20first%20times%20the%20DoD%20has%20relied%20on%20the%20Osprey%20for%20sonobuoy%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaj.%20Sean%20T.%20Penczak%2C%20the%20executive%20officer%20of%20Marine%20Medium%20Tiltrotor%20Squadron%20162%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Osprey's%20unique%20capabilities%20as%20a%20tiltrotor%20aircraft%20allow%20it%20to%20excel%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20distributed%20aviation%20operations%20and%20expeditionary%20advanced%20base%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navy%20sonobuoy%20P-3C%20Orion%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cd184f1021b4c71bc586b45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPetty%20Officer%202nd%20Class%20Jamar%20Fulton%20and%20Airman%20Adam%20Hill%2C%20aviation%20ordnancemen%2C%20load%20sonobuoys%20before%20flight%20operations%20on%20a%20P-3C%20Orion%20in%20Okinawa%2C%20Japan%2C%20August%2027%2C%202011.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%2FPetty%20Officer%202nd%20Class%20Julian%20R.%20Moorefield%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20ability%20to%20cover%20long%20ranges%20with%20a%20payload%20comparable%20to%20the%20P-8%2C%20while%20maximizing%20time%20on%20station%20for%20time-critical%20tasking%2C%20has%20made%20it%20highly%20effective%20in%20the%20anti-submarine%20warfare%20arena%E2%80%94%20demonstrating%20its%20versatility%20and%20value%20as%20emerging%20threats%20continue%20to%20evolve%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20Osprey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20aircraft%20Penczak%20referenced%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boeing.com%2Fdefense%2Fp-8-poseidon%23overview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoeing's%20P-8%20Poseidon%20airplane%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20civilian%20737-800%20and%20was%20created%20for%20maritime%20missions%20like%20anti-sub