ociation%20with%20technology%2C%20said%20Megan%20Lazovick%2C%20VP%20of%20Edison%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20a%20controversial%20move%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20hosts%20and%20presenters%2C%20and%20hosts%20would%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20in%20the%20way%20they%20use%20AI%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20like%20it%20goes%20right%20along%20with%20his%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237d87144-23b2-43a1-9784-5e40f4c6bd49%5C%22%3EFlightStory%20Studio%20has%20built%20a%20diversified%20revenue%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221659%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christiana%20Brenton%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Georgie%20Holt%20helped%20found%20FlightStory%20Studio.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887c8dbf748d8c055f6658b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221106%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristiana%20Brenton%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Georgie%20Holt%20founded%20FlightStory%20Studio%20with%20Bartlett.%3Cp%3EFlightStory%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20just%20one%20way%20FlightStory%20Studio%20is%20trying%20to%20crack%20the%20code%20to%20turn%20creators%20into%20multifaceted%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBartlett%20launched%20%26quot%3BDOAC%26quot%3B%20in%202017%20and%2C%20in%202023%2C%20teamed%20up%20with%20Holt%20and%20Brenton%20to%20launch%20FlightStory%20Studio%20to%20invest%20in%20creators'%20podcasts%20they%20think%20have%20potential%20to%20become%20big%20brands%20in%20their%20own%20right%2C%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20acquiring%20them%20outright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDOAC%26quot%3B%20still%20makes%20up%20most%20of%20the%20company's%20revenue%2C%20but%20it's%20branched%20out%20with%20other%20creators%20like%20Davina%20McCall%2C%20who%20speaks%20to%20the%20midlife%20experience%2C%20and%20relationships%20podcaster%20Paul%20Brunson.%20Today%2C%20FlightStory%20Studio%20owns%20and%20produces%20five%20podcasts%20and%20is%20building%20franchises%20arou