r%20part%20of%20a%20day%20hunched%20over%20a%20fire.%20If%20you're%20a%20smoke%20enthusiast%2C%20opt%20for%20an%20offset%20or%20charcoal-powered%20smoker%20but%20be%20prepared%20for%20a%20learning%20curve.%20Otherwise%2C%20a%20pellet%20grill%20will%20get%20you%20good%20flavor%20(albeit%20not%20quite%20as%20smoky)%20and%20is%20almost%20entirely%20hands-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Most%20grills%20have%20to%20live%20outside%2C%20and%20while%20a%20cover%20is%20a%20worthy%20investment%2C%20even%20the%20best%20smokers%20are%20still%20going%20to%20have%20to%20withstand%20the%20elements.%20Flimsier%20metals%20and%20cheap%20wheels%20were%20immediately%20disqualified.%20Thicker%20steel%20and%20industrial-grade%20casters%20were%20positive%20points%2C%20especially%20for%20competitively%20priced%20smokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELook%20for%20a%20warranty%20of%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%20but%20be%20prepared%20to%20make%20some%20concessions.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20a%20grill%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20materials%20and%20build.%20It's%20hard%20to%20call%20in%20a%20warranty%20on%20something%20like%20a%20grill%20or%20smoker%20because%20%26quot%3Bnormal%20wear%20and%20tear%26quot%3B%20involves%20starting%20fires%2C%20spilling%20grease%2C%20and%20exposure%20to%20the%20elements.%20We%20find%20that%20investing%20in%20a%20grill%20that's%20built%20to%20last%20is%20ultimately%20the%20better%20consideration%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20forgoing%20a%20longer%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a9f8372-6aa1-4f4e-905b-89de4e474a6c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20the%20best%20smokers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20of%20assorted%20meat%20spread%20across%20and%20smoking%20atop%20a%20grill%20grate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6452b4dbb4a8cd00187aa47a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20tested%20the%20best%20smokers%20by%20cooking%20chicken%20drumsticks%20and%20a%20pork%20shoulder%20roast.%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20assembling%20the%20best%20smokers%2C%20analyzing%20the%20design%20and%20structure%2C%20and%20preseasoning%20them%2C%20we%20run%20several%20cooking%20tests%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPork%20shoulder%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%205-%20to%207-pound%20shoulders%2C%20we%20targeted%20225%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20about%20one%20hour%20per%20pound%2C%20checking%20for%20a%20good%20smoke%20ring%20and%20even%20heat%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChicken%20drumsticks%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20evenly%20spaced%20drumsticks%20across%20each%20grill%20to%20test%20for%20the%20level%20of%20smokiness%20and%20doneness.%20(On%20smaller%20grills%2C%20we%20used%20as%20few%20as%20six%20drumsticks%2C%20while%20larger%20models%20saw%2012-18.)%20We%20targeted%20250%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20for%20an%20hour-and-a-half%20cook%20time.%20We%20also%20tossed%20in%20the%20occasional%20full%20bird%20for%20about%20two-and-a-half%20hours%20on%20larger%20grills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZucchini%20strips%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20350%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20we%20spread%20strips%20of%20zucchini%20across%20each%20grill%20to%20look%20for%20char%20marks%20to%20make%20sure%20grills%20were%20cooking%20evenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20consulted%20several%20experts%2C%20including%20chef%20Shola%20Olunloyo%20of%20Studio%20Kitchen%20and%20veteran%20author%20and%20Barbecue%20University%20TV%20host%20Steven%20Raichlen%2C%20to%20find%20out%20what%20makes%20a%20good%20smoker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224cbbac4d-7ede-4281-be1d-7e7d8ba1fddc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EBarbecue%20smoker%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%