122960263.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-world-tariff-would-be-somewhere-in-15-20-range%2Famp_articleshow%2F122960263.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20wants%20to%20speed%20up%20Rupert%20Murdoch's%20deposition%20because%20the%20media%20mogul%20is%2094%20and%20had%20'health%20scares'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Murdoch%20and%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c75af8c262898189409a552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222187%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMurdoch%20and%20then%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20Trump%20International%20Golf%20Links%20in%20Aberdeen%2C%20Scotland%20in%202016.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FCarlo%20Allegri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20wants%20to%20depose%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20ASAP.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20lawyers%20said%20the%20media%20mogul%20is%2094%20and%20has%20had%20%26quot%3Bhealth%20scares.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20involves%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20article%20on%20Trump's%20ties%20to%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20wants%20to%20depose%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Trump's%20lawyers%20asked%20a%20federal%20judge%20to%20force%20Murdoch%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20deposition%20for%20his%20lawsuit%20on%20an%20expedited%20basis%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20News%20Corp.%20executive%20is%2094%20years%20old%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Brecent%20significant%20health%20scares%26quot%3B%20could%20hinder%20his%20ability%20to%20show%20up%20in%20court%20for%20a%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMurdoch%20has%20suffered%2C%20or%20is%20continuing%20to%20suffer%2C%20from%20multiple%20health%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20filing%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20goes%20on%20to%20note%20reports%20that%20Murdoch%20collapsed%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20journalist%20several%20years%20ago%20and%20was%20hospitalized%20after%20getting%20COVID-19%2C%20among%20other%20health%20issues%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20from%20Trump's%20lawyers%20comes%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-murdoch-wall-street-journal-lawsuit-docket-mystery-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20lawsuit%20the%20president%20filed%20against%20Murdoch%20and%20News%20Corp.%20over%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Trump's%20relationship%20with%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Journal%20report%2C%20Trump%20wrote%20a%20%26quot%3Bbawdy%26quot%3B%20letter%20for%20Epstein's%2050th%20birthday%20that%20included%20a%20cryptic%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20Birthday%20%E2%80%94%20and%20may%20every%20day%20be%20another%20wonderful%20secret%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal%2C%20which%20also%20reported%20that%20it%20featured%20an%20illustration%20of%20a%20nude%20woman%20and%20featured%20Trump's%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Journal%20article%20did%20not%20accuse%20Trump%20of%20any%20sexual%20misconduct%20related%20to%20Epstein.%20Epstein's%2050th%20birthday%2C%20in%202003%2C%20was%20well%20before%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20sex%20crimes%20and%20registered%20as%20a%20sex%20offender.%20Epstein%20died%20in%20jail%20in%202019%20while%20awaiting%20trial%20on%20a%20separate%20set%20of%20criminal%20charges%20for%20sex%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lawsuit%20says%20the%20Journal%20%26quot%3Bconcocted%20this%20story%20to%20malign%20President%20Trump's%20character%20and%20integrity%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20authentic%20letter%20or%20drawing%20exists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20purported%20letter%20in%20the%20Article%20somehow%20actually%20exists%2C%20which%20it%20does%20not%2C%20and%20the%20Defendants%20have%20it%20in%20their%20possession%2C%20which%20they%20do%20not%2C%20Murdoch%20has%20easy%20access%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump's%20attorneys%20wrote%20in%20their%20Monday%20filing%20requesting%20an%20expedited%20deposition%20of%20Murdoch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Journal%20has%20said%20it%20stands%20by%20its%20reporting.%20A%20News%20Corp.%20spokesperson%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20about%20Trump's%20Monday%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Darrin%20Gayles%2C%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20defamation%20lawsuit%20in%20Miami%20federal%20court%2C%20asked%20Murdoch%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20request%20for%20an%20expedited%20deposition%20by%20August%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Trump%20told%20journalists%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreach%26quot%3B%20with%20Epstein%20because%20the%20pedophile%20hired%20employees%20who%20had%20worked%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20stole%20people%20that%20worked%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Don't%20ever%20do%20that%20again.'%20He%20did%20it%20again%2C%20and%20I%20threw%20him%20out%20of%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20persona%20non%20grata.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-speed-rupert-murdoch-deposition-old-health-scares-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753728958000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6887c2803d5881a51c1e1cea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-speed-rupert-murdoch-deposition-old-health-scares-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump's%20legal%20team%20wants%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20deposition%20ASAP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A224%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-speed-ru