ch%2C%20Fort%20Lauderdale%2C%20or%20Delray.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20we%20shipped%20our%20car%20stuffed%20with%20bags%20down%20to%20Aventura%20in%20December%2C%20I%20quickly%20realized%20this%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-that-surprised-floridian-about-brooklyn-new-york-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efar%20different%20from%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262689fb4-4ea7-4cee-a4fb-86aeefa06eca%5C%22%3EI%20tried%20to%20make%20the%20most%20out%20of%20it%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20week%2C%20my%20hubby%20was%20gleeful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flucy-kovalova-shares-tips-for-beginner-pickleball-players-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplaying%20pickleball%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20snoozing%20on%20the%20terrace.%20I%2C%20however%2C%20immediately%20experienced%20a%20rosacea%20flareup%20from%20the%2085-degree%20heat%20and%20humidity%20and%20wound%20up%20at%20a%20dermatologist's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20sun.%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20write%20me%20a%20prescription%20to%20go%20back%20to%20New%20York%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20responded.%20Instead%2C%20she%20sold%20me%20%24159%20worth%20of%20sunscreen%20products%20and%20sent%20me%20on%20my%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20weeks%20crawled%20by%2C%20we%20went%20on%20a%20few%20double%20dates%20with%20other%20couples.%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20like%20them.%20They're%20about%20our%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20spouse%20assured%20me.%20They%20were%20%E2%80%94%20give%20or%20take%2020%20years.%20A%20few%20already%20had%20grandchildren%20and%20were%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F67-year-old-runner-workout-tips-after-hip-replacement-longevity-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esecond%20hip%20replacement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20pout%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20my%20situation.%20Every%20day%2C%20I%20would%20don%20a%20wide-brimmed%20baseball%20hat%20and%20take%20a%20long%20walk%20around%20the%20exercise%20trail%20leading%20around%20the%20golf%20course.%20As%20I%20logged%20in%20my%2010%2C000%20steps%2C%20I%20dodged%20kids%20on%20bikes%2C%20Door%20Dash%20deliveries%20on%20motorized%20scooters%2C%20even%20a%20four-foot-long%20lizard%20and%20a%20family%20of%20wild%20ducks.%20Once%2C%20on%20my%20second%20loop%2C%20I%20passed%20a%20woman%20pushing%20her%20Maltese%20in%20a%20stroller.%20I%20peered%20inside%20the%20carriage%3B%20the%20dog%20looked%20more%20miserable%20than%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8317418-0272-4cb6-92bb-4a5a4dc2a92e%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20out%20of%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStrolling%20back%20through%20the%20security%20gates%20into%20the%20condo%20complex%20driveway%2C%20I%20called%20a%20friend%20to%20vent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20so%20not%20me!%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20in%20the%20Twilight%20Zone!%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20to%20hear%20while%20complaining%20about%20how%20no%20one%20wore%20black.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20talking%20me%20off%20the%20ledge%20when%20I%20suddenly%20heard%20screeching%20tires.%20I%20turned%20to%20see%20a%20blue%20Cadillac%20coming%20straight%20at%20me.%20It%20swerved%20side%20to%20side%20wildly%2C%20hitting%20a%20few%20palm%20trees%20in%20its%20path%20and%20taking%20out%20the%20arm%20of%20the%20security%20gate.%20I%20screamed%20and%20jumped%20into%20a%20bush%20as%20it%20sped%20past%2C%20finally%20coming%20to%20a%20hard%20stop%20in%20front%20of%20the%20condo%20fountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ran%20after%20the%20car%2C%20prepared%20to%20scream%20at%20the%20driver%20for%20trying%20to%20mow%20me%20down.%20An%20old%2C%20bent-over%20gentleman%20emerged%20from%20behind%20the%20wheel%2C%20and%20his%20nurse%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20passenger%20side.%20She%20apologized%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20that%20the%20man%20was%20clearly%20in%20shock%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%2097%20years%20old%2C