ment%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn%E2%80%99t%20conducive%20in%20present-day%20settings.%20These%20structures%20need%20frequent%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%2C%20a%20challenge%20that%20modern%20homeowners%20may%20not%20be%20up%20for.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20people%20in%20the%20past%20would%20have%20annual%20gatherings%20during%20the%20harvest%20season%20where%20the%20entire%20extended%20families%20would%20come%20together%20and%20replaster%20the%20walls%20with%20lime.%20This%20does%20not%20happen%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20discarding%20cement%20as%20a%20material%20completely%2C%20it%20is%20vital%20to%20respect%20it%2C%20notes%20Anirudh%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20construction%20comprises%20around%205%20to%207%20percent%20of%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20architecture%20inside%20the%20property%20is%20a%20blend%20of%20contemporary%20and%20vernacular%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-300x142.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-500x237.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-768x364.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-1536x728.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F11_11zon-1697108641-2048x971.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%