0Taimuria%2C%20and%20Ramkela%E2%80%94now%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20niche%20markets%20and%20fetching%20better%20prices%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Deshmukh%2C%20who%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20Cawasji%20Patel%20mango%20while%20nurturing%20his%20orchard%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20sums%20it%20up%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20discovered%20something%20truly%20unique%20in%20my%20mango%20collection%E2%80%94something%20no%20one%20else%20has%E2%80%94I%20intend%20to%20propagate%20it.%20Not%20every%20action%20stems%20from%20commercial%20gain%3B%20sometimes%2C%20you%20do%20it%20purely%20out%20of%20love.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753669800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCourtesy-Springers-The-Mango-Genome_11zon-1753443568.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D476134%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20grown%20across%20Powai%20and%20Thane%20and%20favoured%20by%20the%20British%2C%20the%20rare%20Cawasji%20Patel%20mango%E2%80%94named%20after%20a%20philanthropist%20who%20helped%20shape%20Mumbai%E2%80%94is%20making%20a%20comeback%20on%20a%20Maharashtra%20farm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hiren%20Kumar%20Bose%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F476134%2Fcawasji-patel-rare-mango-maharashtra-mumbai-history%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Trump%20wants%20the%20US%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20mineral-rich%20DR%20Congo's%20peace%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753660792000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Faf90%2Flive%2F9ffb6dd0-6876-11f0-af20-030418be2ca5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcew0vzl7rwjo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20president%20is%20sp